        <body>
            <entry xml:id="entry_art" xml:lang="os">
                <form type="lemma"><orth>art</orth></form>
                <sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                        <q>огонь</q>
                    </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                        <q>fire</q>
                    </abv:tr></sense>
                <abv:exampleGrp>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>arxajy jæ artyl īw sawdæræg ūs</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>возится над огнем женщина в трауре</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>a woman in mourning over the fire</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>43</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>art banʒærstoj qædy</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>развели костер в лесу</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>they made a fire in the forest</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Munk."/><biblScope>60</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>K˳yrdalægon yn zaǧta: „æz dæ bajsærdin, fælæ dy basūʒʒynæ
                            arty“</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>Курдалагон сказал: «я закалил бы тебя, но ты сгоришь в огне»</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>Kurdalagon said: “I would temper you, but you will burn in fire”</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ОЭ"/><biblScope>I 18</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>xūrmæ dær næ xūs kæny, artmæ dær næ</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>не сохнет ни на солнце, ни на огне</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>it dries neither in the sun nor on fire</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ОТ"
                            /><biblScope>32%l25%l</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>cyraǧ æmæ art nyxx˳yssyn kæn, xæʒary rūxs k˳yd næwal wa, aftæ</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>загаси лучину и огонь, чтобы в доме не было больше света</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>extinguish the splinter and fire so that there is no more light in
                                the house</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ОЭ"/><biblScope>I 88</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>K˳ycykk artyl arxajdta, mæqījy sæddæntæ artyl ænʒærsta</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>Куцык возился с огнем, подкладывал в огонь обломки сапетки</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>Kutsyk fiddled with the fire, put the pieces of skep on the fire</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Сека"/><biblScope>75</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>arti qwæcæmæ xanī kosgutæ ærcudæncæ</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>на дым костра пришли слуги хана</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>the khan's servants came to the smoke of the fire</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_MSt."
                            /><biblScope>12%l3%l</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>mæ arti wazal!</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>гибель (остывание) моего очага!</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>the death (the cooling) of my hearth!</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> (выражение ужаса, отчаяния)</note>
                        <note type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (an expression of horror,
                            despair)</note>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Iræf"/><biblScope>89</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>dæ art æmæ xsonæj zyng acæǧd</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>твоим огнивом и кремнем высеки огонь</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>strike fire from your flint with your fire steel</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ЮОПам."/><biblScope>III
                            48</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <re>
                    <form type="lemma"><orth>artag</orth></form>
                    <sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>топливо</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>fuel</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>горючее</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>petrol</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                    <abv:exampleGrp>
                        <abv:example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                            <usg><lang/></usg>
                            <quote>artag afojnadæbæl sæ kʼoxi ne ʽftudæj</quote>
                            <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>горючее не попадало к ним вовремя</q>
                            </abv:tr>
                            <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>fuel did not reach them on time</q>
                            </abv:tr>
                            <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_FS"/><biblScope>V
                                65</biblScope></bibl>
                        </abv:example>
                    </abv:exampleGrp>
                </re>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Закономерная перестановка из %i*atr%i (ср. <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_fyrt"/> ‘сын’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_7rtæ"/> ‘три’);
                    восходит к <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/>
                        <w>*ātar-, *аϑr-</w>
                        <gloss><q>огонь</q></gloss></mentioned>; ср. <mentioned xml:lang="ku"><lang/>
                        <w>ār</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ps"><lang/>
                        <w>or</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="prc"><lang/>
                        <w>âṛ</w></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Morgenstierne._IIFL"/><biblScope>I 235</biblScope></bibl>),
                        <mentioned xml:lang="yai"><lang/>
                        <w>āl</w>
                        <gloss><q>огонь</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="x-rushani"><lang/>
                        <w>arϑōn</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> (←
                            %i*aϑr-dāna%i)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (←
                            %i*aϑr-dāna%i)</note>
                        <gloss><q>очаг</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="x-rushani"
                            ><w>aϑēr</w>
                        <gloss><q>зола</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="x-rushani"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>пепел</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_РТ"/><biblScope>57</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned
                        xml:lang="mnj"><lang/>
                        <w>yūṛ</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="zza"><lang/>
                        <w>adir</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>aδar</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="pal"><lang/>
                        <w>aδur, atur</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="zkh"><lang/>
                        <w>’rw</w></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Henning._Khwar."
                            /><biblScope>13</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>*ātr-(ʼʼtr), *ārt (ʼrδ)</w></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Reichelt"/><biblScope>ZIIIV 247</biblScope></bibl>. —
                            <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Morgenstierne._IIFL"/><biblScope>II
                            273</biblScope></bibl>), %bкушан.%b <mentioned xml:lang=""><lang/>
                        <w>ΑΘΡΟ</w></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_JRAS"
                            /><biblScope xml:lang="ru">1953, стр. 110</biblScope><biblScope
                            xml:lang="en">1953, p. 110</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>ātar-, āϑr-</w>
                        <gloss><q>огонь</q></gloss></mentioned>. В %bскифском%b собственном имени
                        <mentioned xml:lang="xsc"><lang/>
                        <w>Ίατραγόρας</w></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Латышев"
                            /><biblScope>II 56</biblScope></bibl>), может быть, можно видеть в
                    первой части %i*atr%i ‘огонь’, а во второй — <mentioned xml:lang="os"><lang/>
                        <w>agur-</w>
                        <gloss><q>искать</q></gloss></mentioned>. Ср. <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_ærtxūron"/>, д. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærtdor"
                            />.%n<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._ОЭ"/><biblScope>II
                            49</biblScope></bibl>; <bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._Gr."/><biblScope>41</biblScope></bibl>. —
                            <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Hübschmann._Oss."
                            /><biblScope>24</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_ОЯФ_I"/><biblScope>52, 158, 213</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">A regular inversion from %i*atr%i (cf. <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_fyrt"/> ‘son’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_7rtæ"/> ‘three’);
                    traces back to <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/>
                        <w>*ātar-, *аϑr-</w>
                        <gloss><q>fire</q></gloss></mentioned>; cf. <mentioned xml:lang="ku"><lang/>
                        <w>ār</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ps"><lang/>
                        <w>or</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="prc"><lang/>
                        <w>âṛ</w></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Morgenstierne._IIFL"/><biblScope>I 235</biblScope></bibl>),
                        <mentioned xml:lang="yai"><lang/>
                        <w>āl</w>
                        <gloss><q>fire</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="x-rushani"><lang/>
                        <w>arϑōn</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> (←
                            %i*aϑr-dāna%i)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (←
                            %i*aϑr-dāna%i)</note>
                        <gloss><q>hearth</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="x-rushani"
                            ><w>aϑēr</w>
                        <gloss><q>ash</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="x-rushani"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>ashes</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_РТ"/><biblScope>57</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned
                        xml:lang="mnj"><lang/>
                        <w>yūṛ</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="zza"><lang/>
                        <w>adir</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>aδar</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="pal"><lang/>
                        <w>aδur, atur</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="zkh"><lang/>
                        <w>’rw</w></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Henning._Khwar."
                            /><biblScope>13</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>*ātr-(ʼʼtr), *ārt (ʼrδ)</w></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Reichelt"/><biblScope>ZIIIV 247</biblScope></bibl>. —
                            <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Morgenstierne._IIFL"/><biblScope>II
                            273</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned xml:lang="xbc"><lang/>
                        <w>ΑΘΡΟ</w></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_JRAS"
                            /><biblScope xml:lang="ru">1953, стр. 110</biblScope><biblScope
                            xml:lang="en">1953, p. 110</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>ātar-, āϑr-</w>
                        <gloss><q>огонь</q></gloss></mentioned>. In a %bScythian%b proper name
                        <mentioned xml:lang="xsc"><lang/>
                        <w>Ίατραγόρας</w></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Латышев"
                            /><biblScope>II 56</biblScope></bibl>), may be %i*atr%i ‘fire’ in the
                    first part, and <mentioned xml:lang="os"><lang/>
                        <w>agur-</w>
                        <gloss><q>look for</q></gloss></mentioned>in the second part. Cf. <ref
                        type="xr" target="#entry_ærtxūron"/>, Digor <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_ærtdor"/>.%n<bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._ОЭ"/><biblScope>II 49</biblScope></bibl>;
                            <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._Gr."
                            /><biblScope>41</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Hübschmann._Oss."/><biblScope>24</biblScope></bibl>. —
                            <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_ОЯФ_I"/><biblScope>52, 158,
                            213</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
            </entry>
        </body>
